snippet.title: Apple Sauce Apartments - A surreal body horror game about harvesting rent from the moldy apple folk!
snippet.description:
Download for free on itch.io https://shallow-lagoon.itch.io/apple-sauce-apartments?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt Welcome to Apple Sauce Apartments, a spacious low cost living complex situated in the most desirable of rural locations!

Become part of the lively community, bask in the joys of a truly unique shared accommodation.

Experience true convenience, a space to unwind your body and mind!
